{"tid":116166,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬年薪地鐵CEO梁國權,  主席馬時亨應唔應該引疚辭職?","createTime":"2017-02-11T07:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T07:59:05.000Z","uid":82646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e81352ab357b508fe47609cce7e4cd415eb08bbd","tid":116166,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:19:59.000Z","msg":"現場可見minions 尻企, on99唔知自己做乜<br />\n市民疏散非常混亂<br />\n無人踩人大量傷亡純屬好彩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">馬時亨<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span></span>現年63歲，2013年7月以來出任港鐵獨立非執董。<br />\n每年可收取<span style=\"color: red;\">120萬港元袍金<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升任港鐵CEO後加薪35%　<span style=\"color: red;\">梁國權年薪1400萬<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span></span><br />\n<br />\n去年錄得近130億元盈利的港鐵，連續第7年加價。港鐵昨日公布的年報顯示，行政總裁梁國權2015年獲大幅加薪，計及花紅、津貼等等，去年初正式坐正的梁國權，總計年薪高達1410萬元，比起他2014年的1040萬元（當時梁國權分別任職港鐵財務及業務拓展總監以及署理行政總裁），加薪35%。<br />\n<br />\n梁國權2014年的職位為財務及業務拓展總監，8月起擔任署理行政總裁，直至2015年3月才坐正做行政總裁。年報顯示，梁國權坐正後即獲大幅加薪。計及津貼、退休金計劃供款、以及與表現掛鈎的薪酬等，梁國權的總年薪由2014年年薪1040萬元，急升至去年的1410萬元。其中，與表現掛鈎的薪酬部份加幅更接近1倍，由2014年的230萬元急升至450萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%8D%87%E4%BB%BB%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5ceo%E5%BE%8C%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA35-%E6%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E6%AC%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA1400%E8%90%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%258D%2587%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5ceo%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA35-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA1400%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=a910d67b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Ffinance%2F%25E5%258D%2587%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5ceo%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%258A%25A0%25E8%2596%25AA35-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2596%25AA1400%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&h=28974988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/finance/%E5%8D%87%E4%BB%BB%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5ceo%E5%BE%8C%E5%8A%A0%E8%96%AA35-%E6%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E6%AC%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%96%AA1400%E8%90%AC/</a>"},{"pid":"e680768ba8b0164dace1d49ed032b007ec578b68","tid":116166,"uid":75281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"今次純屬不幸既意外，乃單一事件，冇人需要為此問責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bd46f671474bc75e1f9447689def0c53d4e979","tid":116166,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29575ab17dd8e1316799dcdcb68bde63485004bc","tid":116166,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:59:05.000Z","msg":"應該辭職，但唔關今次件事"}]}